window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This M/M romance bundle contains four seasonal romances from award-winning author Isobel Starling.</p> <p><i>Back Where He Belongs</i> (M/M puppy-play novella)</p> <p>Kier Campbell returns to Scotland from Australia to spend Christmas with his family. What he finds is a gift that is worth more than money could buy.</p> <p>\"Daddy Christmas\" (daddy-kink short story) </p> <p>Ryan Sutherland is a side character from <i>Detective Fox and the Christmas Caper</i>. This short story gives him the happy ending he deserves.</p> <p><i>The Christmas Bonus </i></p> <p>The Investobank Christmas shindig at the Lorien Hotel puts Jake Walters and the object of his lust in the same place at the same time...and it's Christmas! </p> <p><i>Fred &amp; Ginger</i></p> <p>The Big Boy Cupcakes baker has to rush the last-minute order of cock cupcakes for the party of a celebrity, but in his haste to deliver, he falls foul of an over-keen chocolate Labrador named Fred, and his handsome owner....</p>"; 
